related_questions.question: Are solar powered battery chargers any good?
related_questions.snippet: The good thing with solar chargers however is that they are pretty low powered – that's why they are perfect as trickle, or maintenance, chargers. related_questions.question: What is solar panel battery charger?
related_questions.snippet: A solar charger is a charger that employs solar energy to supply electricity to devices or batteries. They are generally portable. Solar chargers can charge lead acid or Ni-Cd battery banks up to 48 V and hundreds of ampere-hours (up to 4000 Ah) capacity.
